i><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;Her pulse seems steady now, the rhythmic beeps feeling almost... antagonistic at this point.</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;She takes a deep breath.</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;&quot;ANON... THANK YOU.  BUT... WHY?&quot;</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;&quot;Why?  Because, Kitten, I care about you.  A lot.  I made a promise to get you out of here safely, and I will fulfill that promise no matter what.  You deserve to live your life.&quot;</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;&quot;...EVEN THOUGH I&#039;M A MONSTER?&quot;</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;&quot;You are no monster.  You&#039;re a victim of some kind of experiment.  You are probably one of the least monstrous people I have ever met.&quot;</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;&quot;...THANK YOU...&quot;</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;She shakes slightly in fear, clutching you tightly.  Her claws gently dig into your back.</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;You don&#039;t mind in the slightest.</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;&quot;You&#039;re worth it.&quot;</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;&quot;...I... AM WORTH... YOUR CARE?&quot;</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;&quot;Of course.&quot;</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;She stares at you, terminal whirring.</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;&quot;........ANON.  YOU ARE... THE KINDEST MAN I HAVE EVER MET.&quot;</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;She buries her screen in your shoulder again, choking out more &quot;sobs&quot; as her speakers fizz again.</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;&quot;THANK YOU.  THANK YOU THANK YOU THANK YOU.&quot;</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;You wrap your arms around her, feeling her smooth black fur stand on end.  She still feels so fragile...</div></li